<br>
One of the key things for me was killing massive numbers of goblins and orcs in Misty Thicket and turning in their necklaces and belts.  Eventually, I got the Squad Ring with rechargable Healing.  Saved my butt more than once as it can be used on the run and gives 85 hp of healing, I believe.  Also, if you get heavily beaten, don't have a cleric and can make it back to Rivervale, you can get back to full health by doing the heal, recharge cycle repeatedly.  You can get info on the Squad Ring from Allakhazam's Site:  <!--EZCODE AUTOLINK START--><a href="http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=63">eqdb.allakhazam.com/quest.html?quest=63</a><!--EZCODE AUTOLINK END--><br>
<br>
